## 1. INTRODUCTION
[cite_start]The Rainfall Prediction App is a desktop-based application developed to forecast monthly rainfall. [cite_start]The prediction model in this application employs the Tsukamoto Fuzzy Inference System (FIS) optimized using a Genetic Algorithm (GA). [cite_start]The system processes historical climate data—comprising attributes such as temperature, air humidity, air pressure, wind velocity, and rainfall—to generate accurate forecasts and evaluate the Mean Absolute Percentage Error (MAPE). 

## 2. HARDWARE & SOFTWARE REQUIREMENTS
